Usage: create_ccopt_clock_tree [-help] [-name <clockname>] -source <pin>
                               [-stop_at_sdc_clock_roots] [ -no_skew_group ]

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
-name <clockname>                 # user-defined identifier for this clock tree
                                  # (string, optional)
-no_skew_group                    # do not define any default skew group for
                                  # the clock (bool, optional)
-source <pin>                     # source pin for the clock tree
                                  # ((instTerm|term), required)
-stop_at_sdc_clock_roots          # stop searching for parts of the clock tree
                                  # through SDC clock roots (bool, optional)